nt-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: common-ligatures;\">设置代理：127.0.0.1为HTTP代理服务器地址</span><br style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: common-ligatures;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: common-ligatures;\">1080为HTTP代理服务器端口</span><br style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: common-ligatures;\"><img  class=\"img-fluid\"  src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200401153551766.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2tvbmdzYW5qaW4=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" style=\"margin: 24px 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: common-ligatures;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: common-ligatures;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: common-ligatures;\">设置完进行重启，即可解决</span>', '2020-05-28 08:35:49', 4, 1, 1);
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (25, 'Android Studio通过Android Device Monitor查看SharedPreferences文件以及遇到的问题', '<h3>首先你要了解到：</h3><p>Android Device Monitor&nbsp;<strong>已在 Android Studio 3.1 中弃用，并已从 Android Studio 3.2 中移除</strong>。</p><p>官方文档，以及替用组件：<a data-cke-saved-href=\"https://developer.android.google.cn/studio/profile/monitor.html\" href=\"https://developer.android.google.cn/studio/profile/monitor.html\">https://developer.android.google.cn/studio/profile/monitor.html</a></p><p><span tabindex=\"-1\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-cke-widget-wrapper=\"1\" data-cke-filter=\"off\" class=\"cke_widget_wrapper cke_widget_inline cke_widget_image cke_image_nocaption cke_widget_selected\" data-cke-display-name=\"图像\" data-cke-widget-id=\"5\" role=\"region\" aria-label=\" 图像 小部件\"><img  class=\"img-fluid\"  alt=\"\" height=\"531\" data-cke-saved-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200321212416232.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2tvbmdzYW5qaW4=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200321212416232.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2tvbmdzYW5qaW4=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" width=\"586\" data-cke-widget-data=\"{&amp;quot;hasCaption&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;src&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200321212416232.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2tvbmdzYW5qaW4=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;alt&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;width&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;586&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;height&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;531&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;lock&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;align&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;none&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;classes&amp;quot;:[]}\" data-cke-widget-upcasted=\"1\" data-cke-widget-keep-attr=\"0\" data-widget=\"image\" class=\"cke_widget_element\"><span class=\"cke_reset cke_widget_drag_handler_container\" style=\"background: url(&quot;https://csdnimg.cn/release/blog_editor_html/release1.6.7/ckeditor/plugins/widget/images/handle.png&quot;) rgba(220, 220, 220, 0.5); top: -15px; left: 0px; display: block;\"><img  class=\"img-fluid\"  class=\"cke_reset cke_widget_drag_handler\" data-cke-widget-drag-handler=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPABAP///wAAACH5BAEKAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" width=\"15\" title=\"点击并拖拽以移动\" height=\"15\" role=\"presentation\" draggable=\"true\"></span><span class=\"cke_image_resizer\" title=\"点击并拖拽以改变尺寸\">​</span></span></p><p>&nbsp;但是可以从你的<strong>SDK</strong>的安装路径下启动Android Device Monitor</p><p><span tabindex=\"-1\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-cke-widget-wrapper=\"1\" data-cke-filter=\"off\" class=\"cke_widget_wrapper cke_widget_inline cke_widget_image cke_image_nocaption cke_widget_selected\" data-cke-display-name=\"图像\" data-cke-widget-id=\"4\" role=\"region\" aria-label=\" 图像 小部件\"><img  class=\"img-fluid\"  alt=\"\" height=\"476\" data-cke-saved-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200321213109883.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2tvbmdzYW5qaW4=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200321213109883.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2tvbmdzYW5qaW4=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" width=\"650\" data-cke-widget-data=\"{&amp;quot;hasCaption&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;src&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200321213109883.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2tvbmdzYW5qaW4=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;alt&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;width&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;650&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;height&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;476&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;lock&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;align&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;none&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;classes&amp;quot;:[]}\" data-cke-widget-upcasted=\"1\" data-cke-widget-keep-attr=\"0\" data-widget=\"image\" class=\"cke_widget_element\"><span class=\"cke_reset cke_widget_drag_handler_container\" style=\"background: url(&quot;https://csdnimg.cn/release/blog_editor_html/release1.6.7/ckeditor/plugins/widget/images/handle.png&quot;) rgba(220, 220, 220, 0.5); top: -15px; left: 0px; display: block;\"><img  class=\"img-fluid\"  class=\"cke_reset cke_widget_drag_handler\" data-cke-widget-drag-handler=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPABAP///wAAACH5BAEKAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" width=\"15\" title=\"点击并拖拽以移动\" height=\"15\" role=\"presentation\" draggable=\"true\"></span><span class=\"cke_image_resizer\" title=\"点击并拖拽以改变尺寸\">​</span></span></p><p>双击路径下<strong>...\\SDK\\tools\\monitor.bat</strong>启动Android Device Monitor</p><p>一切正常则启动成功：<strong>File Explorer标签下/date/date/项目路径/shared_prefs</strong>就能看到生成的*.xml文件了</p><p><span tabindex=\"-1\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-cke-widget-wrapper=\"1\" data-cke-filter=\"off\" class=\"cke_widget_wrapper cke_widget_inline cke_widget_image cke_image_nocaption cke_widget_selected\" data-cke-display-name=\"图像\" data-cke-widget-id=\"3\" role=\"region\" aria-label=\" 图像 小部件\"><img  class=\"img-fluid\"  alt=\"\" height=\"510\" data-cke-saved-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200321214635765.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2tvbmdzYW5qaW4=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200321214635765.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2tvbmdzYW5qaW4=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" width=\"640\" data-cke-widget-data=\"{&amp;quot;hasCaption&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;src&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200321214635765.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2tvbmdzYW5qaW4=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;alt&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;width&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;640&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;height&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;510&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;lock&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;align&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;none&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;classes&amp;quot;:[]}\" data-cke-widget-upcasted=\"1\" data-cke-widget-keep-attr=\"0\" data-widget=\"image\" class=\"cke_widget_element\"><span class=\"cke_reset cke_widget_drag_handler_container\" style=\"background: url(&quot;https://csdnimg.cn/release/blog_editor_html/release1.6.7/ckeditor/plugins/widget/images/handle.png&quot;) rgba(220, 220, 220, 0.5); top: -15px; left: 0px; display: block;\"><img  class=\"img-fluid\"  class=\"cke_reset cke_widget_drag_handler\" data-cke-widget-drag-handler=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPABAP///wAAACH5BAEKAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" width=\"15\" title=\"点击并拖拽以移动\" height=\"15\" role=\"presentation\" draggable=\"true\"></span><span class=\"cke_image_resizer\" title=\"点击并拖拽以改变尺寸\">​</span></span></p><p>也许你也可能像我一样启动Android Device Monitor提示错误，提示查看<strong>...SDK\\tools\\lib\\monitor-x86_64\\configuration\\*.log</strong>日志文件；</p><div tabindex=\"-1\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-cke-widget-wrapper=\"1\" data-cke-filter=\"off\" class=\"cke_widget_wrapper cke_widget_block cke_widget_codeSnippet cke_widget_selected\" data-cke-display-name=\"代码段\" data-cke-widget-id=\"2\" role=\"region\" aria-label=\"代码段 小部件\"><pre data-cke-widget-data=\"{&amp;quot;code&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;!SESSION 2020-03-21 17:29:02.552 -----------------------------------------------\\neclipse.buildId=unknown\\njava.version=10.0.2\\njava.vendor=Oracle Corporation\\nBootLoader constants: OS=win32, ARCH=x86_64, WS=win32, NL=zh_CN\\nCommand-line arguments:  -os win32 -ws win32 -arch x86_64 -data @noDefault\\n.\\n.\\n.\\norg.osgi.framework.BundleException: The bundle \\&amp;quot;org.eclipse.core.runtime_3.8.0.v20120912-155025 [46]\\&amp;quot; could not be resolved. Reason: Missing Constraint: Bundle-RequiredExecutionEnvironment: CDC-1.0/Foundation-1.0,J2SE-1.3\\n.\\n.\\n.\\n!ENTRY org.eclipse.osgi 4 0 2020-03-21 17:29:07.459\\n!MESSAGE Application error\\n!STACK 1\\njava.lang.IllegalStateException: Unable to acquire application service. Ensure that the org.eclipse.core.runtime bundle is resolved and started (see config.ini).&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;classes&amp;quot;:[]}\" data-cke-widget-upcasted=\"1\" data-cke-widget-keep-attr=\"0\" data-widget=\"codeSnippet\" class=\"cke_widget_element\"><code class=\"hljs\">!SESSION 2020-03-21 17:29:02.552 -----------------------------------------------\neclipse.buildId=unknown\njava.version=10.0.2\njava.vendor=Oracle Corporation\nBootLoader constants: OS=win32, ARCH=x86_64, WS=win32, NL=zh_CN\nCommand-line arguments:  -os win32 -ws win32 -arch x86_64 -data @noDefault\n.\n.\n.\norg.osgi.framework.BundleException: The bundle \"org.eclipse.core.runtime_3.8.0.v20120912-155025 [46]\" could not be resolved. Reason: Missing Constraint: Bundle-RequiredExecutionEnvironment: CDC-1.0/Foundation-1.0,J2SE-1.3\n.\n.\n.\n!ENTRY org.eclipse.osgi 4 0 2020-03-21 17:29:07.459\n!MESSAGE Application error\n!STACK 1\njava.lang.IllegalStateException: Unable to acquire application service. Ensure that the org.eclipse.core.runtime bundle is resolved and started (see config.ini).</code></pre><span class=\"cke_reset cke_widget_drag_handler_container\" style=\"background: url(&quot;https://csdnimg.cn/release/blog_editor_html/release1.6.7/ckeditor/plugins/widget/images/handle.png&quot;) rgba(220, 220, 220, 0.5); top: -15px; left: 0px; display: block;\"><img  class=\"img-fluid\"  class=\"cke_reset cke_widget_drag_handler\" data-cke-widget-drag-handler=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPABAP///wAAACH5BAEKAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" width=\"15\" title=\"点击并拖拽以移动\" height=\"15\" role=\"presentation\"></span></div><p>首先上网查了资料，试了别人的方法，但还是没有解决；看到有人说monitor还不支持JDK1.8以上版本；发现自己jdk版本10.0.2；修改为jdk1.8后成功启动</p><p>分享自己查找资料别人的解决方法，错误不同，解决方法不同</p><p><strong>1.jdk版本过高</strong></p><p><strong>2.以管理员身份运行Android Studio</strong></p><p><strong>3.配置环境变量JAVA_HOME：你的jdk安装地址</strong></p><p><strong>4.如果.android文件夹是\"只读\"的，在文件夹上右键-属性-取消掉\"只读\"(我试着取消了，可是再去看属性又标记了只读，不知道是不是错误不一样的原因)</strong></p><p>1和3的错误问题应该是一样的，Android Studio配置的jdk路径版本过高或路径不对。(如果有其他的开发软件用到其他jdk版本，只需重新配一下Android Studio中的路径就可以了，不需要改变JAVA_HOME)</p><h3>配置Android Studio的SDK和JDK默认路径</h3><p>Other Settings - &gt; Default Project Structure...</p><p><span tabindex=\"-1\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-cke-widget-wrapper=\"1\" data-cke-filter=\"off\" class=\"cke_widget_wrapper cke_widget_inline cke_widget_image cke_image_nocaption cke_widget_selected\" data-cke-display-name=\"图像\" data-cke-widget-id=\"1\" role=\"region\" aria-label=\" 图像 小部件\"><img  class=\"img-fluid\"  alt=\"\" height=\"430\" data-cke-saved-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200321221256198.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2tvbmdzYW5qaW4=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200321221256198.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2tvbmdzYW5qaW4=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" width=\"410\" data-cke-widget-data=\"{&amp;quot;hasCaption&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;src&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200321221256198.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2tvbmdzYW5qaW4=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;alt&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;width&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;410&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;height&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;430&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;lock&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;align&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;none&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;classes&amp;quot;:[]}\" data-cke-widget-upcasted=\"1\" data-cke-widget-keep-attr=\"0\" data-widget=\"image\" class=\"cke_widget_element\"><span class=\"cke_reset cke_widget_drag_handler_container\" style=\"background:rgba(220,220,220,0.5);background-image:url(https://csdnimg.cn/release/blog_editor_html/release